"We look forward to seeing you at Coconuts. We pride ourselves in our excellent service and making your visit as enjoyable as possible. Thank you for visiting Coconuts on the Beach." What makes Coconuts so unique and such a great place to dine and drink, is our incredible view overlooking the Atlantic Ocean. While relaxing on our huge, outdoor tiki deck under the warm Florida sun, you can enjoy the sights and sounds of the beach and the local wildlife. Almost daily you can spot porpoises playing in the surf. In addition to the Florida sunshine, ocean breeze, surf and sand, Coconuts is famous for the bathing beauties that frequent the beach right in front of the ocean deck. What more could you ask for?
